If your SparkMAXes (and probably SparkFLEXes too, but I cannot verify this) have a yellow-ish but not always yellow light and flash strangely and inconsistently, the CAN bus is plugged in backwards at some point.

If Phoenix Tuner/TunerX shows one or multiple ‘XalonFX’ the same issue has occurred.
